query: WITH entities AS (SELECT name, id FROM terms_templates WHERE (COALESCE((name, id) > ($3, $2), $2 IS NULL)) ORDER BY name, id LIMIT $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: TermsTemplateId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN terms_template_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.name, i.id, i.id, e.sequence
